text: Rahul Sankrityayan Inter College Rajesultanpur (Rahul Sankrityayan Inter College Rajesultanpur, Hindi: राहुल सास्कृतायन इण्टर कालेज,राजेसुल्तानपुर) is an intermediate college located in Rajesultanpur, Uttar Pradesh. It was established in 1990 by the Government of India. ==References== ==External links== * Education Boards in India * Board of High School and Intermediate Education Uttar Pradesh Category:Intermediate colleges in Uttar Pradesh Category:Education in Ambedkar Nagar district Category:Rajesultanpur Category:Educational institutions established in 1990
